VLRX Total market cap 16M which is downright silly Its the same situation as TNDM about 18 months ago At this share price the market is ASSUMING another secondary offering soon I dont think that happens based on the CEOs comments in last weeks press release The Company now expects to end the second quarter with 27 million in cash and cash equivalents vs the original estimate of 25 million with the Companys current cash position now allowing it to operate into February 2020 assuming no additional capital or nondilutive financing
